# Daegu Metro Network Analysis

## Overview

This repository contains research on the impact of metro network reconfiguration on travel patterns in Daegu, South Korea.

## Research Topics

* Metro network centrality analysis
* Transfer station effects
* Origin-Destination (OD) flow changes
* Mobility hub integration
* Demand Responsive Transport (DRT)

## Methods

* Network Analysis
* NetworkX
* GIS Analysis
* Interrupted Time Series Analysis

## Author

Graduate Researcher
Daegu Transportation Corporation

## Research Period

2023–2026

## Study Area

Daegu Transportation Network

## Key Findings

* Transfer stations became dominant mobility hubs after network expansion.
* Passenger flows shifted toward newly connected corridors.
* Network centrality indicators effectively explained ridership redistribution.

## Future Research

